This paper deals with optimizing the caching of 360$^o$ videos in edge servers to reduce bandwidth requirements. It involves techniques such as virtual viewports, proactive caching, and deep reinforcement learning. Based on these topics, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories are Multimedia (cs.MM), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), and Machine Learning (cs.DL).
